Embbed tomcat for spring mvc

Start the server: mvn tomcat7:run
Stop the server: Ctrl+c

plug in 
<plugin>
	<groupId>org.apache.tomcat.maven</groupId>
	<artifactId>tomcat7-maven-plugin</artifactId>
	<version>2.2</version>

	<configuration>
		<port>9090</port>
		<update>true</update>
	</configuration>

</plugin>

Dependency 

<dependency>
		<groupId>commons-logging</groupId>
		<artifactId>commons-logging</artifactId>
		<version>1.2</version>
</dependency>


